A més OpenTTD s'executa als següents dispositius (tampoc estan mantingudes i poden estar sense actualitzar):
* Apple iPhone / iPod Touch [http://www.zodttd.com/wiki/index.php/OpenTTD.app]
* GP2X [http://wiki.gp2x.org/wiki/OpenTTD]
* Nokia N-series (Maemo) [http://myy.haaga-helia.fi/~a0702483/maemo/] i [http://www.tt-forums.net/viewtopic.php?f=33&t=36042] (des de [http://openttd.toimii.net/maemo/])
* [[Main/es/Nintendo DS]] [http://www.tt-forums.net/viewtopic.php?f=33&t=35306]
* Pocket PC [http://www.esoftinteractive.com/openttd.html]
* PSP [http://openttd.pc-workshop.da.ru/]
* UIQ3 [http://my-symbian.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30981]
* Zaurus PDA [http://zsi2.stonekeep.com/index.php?v=d&a=2127]

